About Us

Ayur Madupur is a high school student with a passion for both medicine and artificial intelligence. He created this website with the guidance of physicians to help people gain early insights into their skin conditions through technology.

Ayur believes in the power of AI to make healthcare more accessible and is continually working on projects that blend science and innovation.
